data.description: Welcome Home!! Less than 3 yrs Newly Renovated! This amazing well maintained home in a cul-da-sac situated on almost an acre lot. This 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom home features an open concept to the Living Room, Kitchen and Dining Room. The large Master Suite includes a walk in closet, double vanity, a huge remodeled shower. Two additional bedrooms are located on the main floor. The lower level offers a large finished bedroom, bathroom with shower. A big laundry room, and secondary living room. This home comes with a big covered back deck that is lovely for huge gatherings. The large leveled fenced in backyard gives privacy for your entertainment. NEW ROOF and Siding replaced less than 2 yrs ago! Plus many more upgrades all done within the last 4 years. It is a must see for yourself!
